Text:
If you can't get it to work with the patch try this:

First open program as Administrator then follow these steps:

1. Install the program.
2. Run the program and click the icon at the top left of the program window.
3. Click Enter SN.
4. Run the keygen.
5. Disconnect from the internet.
6. Type random numbers into the SN box.
7. It will say that it can't connect to webcammax servers and give you options. One of these options is a button that says "Manual". Click it.
8. Copy the machine code into the keygen and click generate.
9. Copy the "Unlock" code that was generated into the "Unlock" box in the program.
10. Click Continue (or whatever it is to enter it) and you're done.
